title: Tested in 2017: Ryan's Favorite Things!
description:
Tested's production coordinator Ryan shares some of his favorite things of 2017, including a favorite backpack, a memorable trip from this year, and something priceless!

Please consider contributing to the ASPCA here: https://www.aspca.org

Shot by Gunther Kirsch
Edited by Joey Fameli
